@node Main "Connexions - Documentation"

                            'Connexions' 1.02

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Connexions' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} where you try to link all the
numbered tiles. The number displayed on each tile indicates the number
of links that start from that tile. The links can be horizontal,
vertical or diagonal, but no link can cross another.

  When the number of links from a tile is the same as the number
displayed on it, the number will turn to white... but that doesn't mean
that the links are placed as they should be on that particular game...

  Have fun!

