@node play "The game: Installation/Playing"

                             Installation

  The installation is very simple, just place "Connexions" where you want on
your hard drive, floppy disk, Ram Disk, etc. No other files or Libraries
are needed.

                             How to play?

  To play, it's very simple: just click on one of the numbered tiles, and
while holding the mousebutton, move the mouse pointer to a @{b}neighbouring@{ub}
tile, then release the mousebutton. If there was no link between the two
tiles, a link will appear there, otherwise that link will disappear. You
can also remove a link by pressing and releasing the mousebutton on the
unwanted link.

  The number displayed on each tile indicates the number of links that
go to that tile. The links can be horizontal, vertical or diagonal, but
no link can cross another, if you try to cross two diagonal links, the
previous one will be replaced by the last one you make.

  When the number of links from a tile is the same as the number
displayed on it, the number will turn to white. Continue to link the
tiles until all their assigned numbers turn to white.

  You can restart the game anytime by clicking on the @{b}New Game@{ub} button.

  Have fun!

